text: Siberia is a 1998 Dutch comedy movie directed by Robert Jan Westdijk and starring Roeland Fernhout, Hugo Metsers, Vlatka Simac, Nicole Eggert, Johnny Lion, Alessia Sorvillo, Francesca Rizzo, Nefeli Anthopoulou. == Other websites == * Category:1998 comedy movies Category:Dutch comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Robert Jan Westdijk
